snippet.title: SIGNALIS - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
SIGNALIS is a classic survival horror experience with a unique aesthetic, full of melancholic mystery. Investigate a dark secret, solve puzzles, fight off nightmarish creatures and navigate dystopian, surreal retrotech worlds.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1262350

Follow us for updates:
SIGNALIS website: http://rose-engine.org/signalis
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/LastStarfarer
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/roseengine/
